creator: Daily Rays
descriptionHtml:
The first thing that you look at sets the stage for your entire day. Why not make it positive, inspirational, and beautiful? Presence helps you become more mindful, present, and happy by showing you positive words, art, and wisdom from the world’s most inspiring people on the world’s first always-visible Inspiration Display.

Presence is a mental wellness system that lets you personalize and place positivity throughout your home, office, and space. The science-backed practice of reading daily affirmations and positive quotations is proven to help you reframe your thinking, reprogram your subconscious, create new neural connections, and form better habits and positive thinking.

Use the Presence App to choose and personalize your viewing experience on the Presence Inspiration Display by selecting Raylists™. Raylists are collections of Rays (individual pieces of words, art, and wisdom) that are delivered to you on a daily consistent basis. Choose from over fourteen unique categories, hundreds of Raylists, and experience thousands of beautiful Rays.

Designed to build resilience, form better habits, and lead a healthier, happier life. Presence brings positivity into your life in a new way that has never been seen before.

Presence has been featured on NBC, CBS, ESPN, Thrive Global:

“One of those things that’s actually good for your soul”
NBC

“A motivational quote board designed to stream positivity into our homes”
CBS

“A unique idea designed to radically change how we get and stay inspired every day”
ESPN

"One of the most anxiously anticipated products of the year"
Thrive Global
